text: Jiří Šefčík (born 14 April 1973) is a Czech rower. He competed in the men's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Czechoslovakia Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Jindřichův Hradec
